org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.CoreElements

Interface Configuration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaAnalysisContext, SaAnalysisContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigurationImpl, GaAnalysisContextImpl, SaAnalysisContextImpl

    public interface Configuration
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Configuration'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Structured Classifier
    • Base Package
    • Mode

    See Also:
    CoreElementsPackage.getConfiguration()
